## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for finance.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers balance visibility,
reservation state,
settlement state,
dispute state,
historical finance reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- finance context must resolve
- holder/control basis must resolve
- settlement/reservation scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid finance context
- invalid balance basis
- invalid settlement path
- invalid disclosure scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish balance state,
reservation state,
settlement state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- finance runtime scope is explicit
- settlement-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
